sknifedatar

library(sknifedatar)
library(timetk)
library(tidyverse)
emae <- sknifedatar::emae_series 

nest_data <- emae %>%
  nest(nested_column = -sector) %>% 
  mutate(ts_plots = map(nested_column, 
                        ~ plot_time_series(.data = .x,
                                           .date_var = date,
                                           .value = value,
                                           .interactive = FALSE,
                                           .line_size = 0.15)
                         ))
